The broader impact here is shifting the evaluation culture in NLP: instead of chasing higher scores on flawed splits, we promote robustness through *design-aware validation*. Given our team’s strength in causal modeling and domain generalization, this isn’t just a data hygiene task—it’s an opportunity to define a new standard for trustworthy evaluation in misinformation research.
