cipate emerging topics, allowing proactive construction of test sets that evaluate zero-shot generalization to novel disinformation themes. By transforming dataset splitting into a generative, causal simulation platform, DynaSplit exposes model fragility to shifting epistemic conditions and closes backdoor paths exploited by current systems. This leads to more reliable metrics, improved model interpretability, and a paradigm shift from benchmarking to *resilience auditing*. The framework is extensible to other domains plagued by temporal and source bias, such as medical misinformation or financial scam detection.",
